to determine the true extent, but this is definitely an indicator that it's worth the

100
00:07:34,621 --> 00:07:41,363
game industry turning their attention to. So I've sort of lumped together online games and social

101
00:07:41,383 --> 00:07:46,524
media so far, but they are of course very, very different, right? And so how do we determine

102
00:07:46,864 --> 00:07:52,505
sort of where in the life cycle of the digital social space online games are versus social media?

