00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:28,021
of hate and harassment is sort of all bundled into one rule.

122
00:09:30,022 --> 00:09:33,862
And in order to sort of get a corollary kind of rule

123
00:09:34,602 --> 00:09:36,323
in social media, you kind of have

