220
00:16:08,153 --> 00:16:11,496
and where we saw Heather Heyer lose her life.

221
00:16:12,317 --> 00:16:19,361
that we saw internet companies really take significant steps to address white supremacy

222
00:16:19,421 --> 00:16:25,904
on their platform and to really rethink their policies. The same was true of the Pittsburgh

223
