Tree of Life shooting in October 2018. So before that, we were telling various internet service

224
00:16:33,709 --> 00:16:40,112
providers that Gab is a bad actor platform that does not engage in content moderation, that does

225
00:16:40,172 --> 00:16:40,332
not...

226
00:16:41,057 --> 00:16:42,818
care about hate speech on his platform.

227
00:16:43,378 --> 00:16:47,180
And it was only after the largest anti-Semitic attack

228
00:16:47,940 --> 00:16:54,003
in American history that various internet service providers

229
00:16:54,063 --> 00:16:55,543
cut off service to Gab.

230
00:16:56,824 --> 00:16:59,665
And the same is true of the Christchurch mosque shooting

231
00:17:00,665 --> 00:17:02,426
in Christchurch, New Zealand in March of 2019,

232
00:17:02,866 --> 00:17:06,688
the Muslim community in Christchurch, New Zealand was attacked

233
00:17:08,957 --> 00:17:11,878
